tachyon.worker.block

Class BlockHeartbeatReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.worker.block.BlockStoreEventListenerBase
      • tachyon.worker.block.BlockHeartbeatReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BlockStoreEventListener

    public final class BlockHeartbeatReporter
extends BlockStoreEventListenerBase
    Represents the delta of the block store within one heartbeat period. For now, newly committed blocks do not pass through this master communication mechanism, instead it is synchronized through BlockDataManager.commitBlock(long, long). This class is thread safe.

      • generateReport

        public BlockHeartbeatReport generateReport()
        Generates the report of the block store delta in the last heartbeat period. Calling this method marks the end of a period and the start of a new heartbeat period.
        Returns:
        the block store delta report for the last heartbeat period
